  </study_design_info>
  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>The estimated treatment difference (elzasonan plus sertraline - sertraline monotherapy) in MADRS (Montgomery-Asberg Depression Rating Scale) remission rates at Week 8 in patients with MDD.</measure>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>Change from baseline in: MADRS, CGI-I, CGI-S, HAMA, HAMD17, CSFQ, SOS-10 and PGID-D total scores at Week 8. Treatment differences in MADRS response rates at Week 8.</measure>
  </secondary_outcome>
